	* enum.c (enum_find, enum_reject): Return an enumerator if no
	  block is given; backported from 1.9.

	* io.c (rb_io_each_line, rb_io_each_byte, rb_io_s_foreach,
	  argf_each_line, argf_each_byte): Ditto.

	* string.c (str_gsub): Ditto.

