	  possible.

	* array.c (rb_ary_pop, rb_ary_pop_m, rb_ary_shift, rb_ary_shift_m):
	  Array#pop and Array#shift can take an optional argument
	  specifying the number of elements to remove and return;
	  backported from 1.9.

