	  OpenSSL::PKey::DH#to_der.

	* ext/openssl/ossl_pkey_dsa.c (ossl_dsa_to_der): new function for
	  OpenSSL::PKey::DSA#to_der.

	* ext/openssl/ossl_pkey_rsa.c (ossl_rsa_to_der): new function for
	  OpenSSL::PKey::RSA#to_der.

